metadata.name: Sunrise at Panabo
metadata.description:
This was my first time to visit this place in the Southern Philippines. I felt calm during that day and I want to convey that feeling of peace and warmth into the photo. I did not have to try hard as the still waters and the warm sun seemed to resonate with my thoughts during that day.

This piece has been published in the Photopills Awards Book of 2020. 

Artist: John Kimwell Laluma
Edition: 1/1 NFT
Dimension: 4000x6000
Date Taken: October 27, 2019
